quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,40,Oh Bantwana baka-Israyeli! Khumbulani ububele bami enganenzela bona bese nifeza isivumelwano sami ukuze ngifeze isivumelwano senu (nami) futhi nesabe mina (kuphela)
  2,41,Futhi nikholelwe kulokho engakwehlisela phansi (izambulo) ukuqinisekisa lokho eninakho futhi ningabi abokuqala abangakholelwa kukona ningashintshi izambulo zami ngokunenzuzo encane (ngokuyize leze) futhi sabani mina
  2,42,Ningasithezi iqiniso ngamanga futhi ningalifihli iqiniso nibe nilazi
  2,43,Futhi yenzani umthandazo ninikele kwabampofu (zakaah) bese nikhothama kanye nalabo abakhothamayo (ekudumiseni uMvelinqangi)
  2,44,Ngakube nitshela abantu ukuthi benze ukulunga bese nizikhohlwa nina nibe ningabafundi bencwadi ngakube aninawo yini umqondo na
  2,45,Futhi celani usizo ngokubekezela nangomthandazo ngempela lokho kunzima ngaphandle kwalabo abazithobayo
  2,46,Labo abacabanga (beqinisekile) ukuthi bona bayohlangana neNkosi yabo futhi yiyona abayophindela kuyo